Raymond AGUILAR, Petitioner,
v.
UNITED STATES Sammy Nichols, Petitioner,
v.
United States. No. 19-5315 Supreme Court of the United States. January 13, 2020 Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Tenth Circuit denied. Justice Sotomayor, with whom Justice Ginsburg joins, dissenting from the denial of certiorari: I dissent for the reasons set out in Brown v. United States , 586 U.S. ----, 139 S.Ct. 14 , 202 L.Ed.2d 302 (2018) ( Sotomayor, J., dissenting).
